{"id":1236868943,"question_id":9,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1713558730,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1236868943/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Palindrome Number","memory":"43.8 MB","code":"public class Solution {\n    public boolean isPalindrome(int x) {\n        if (x < 0 || (x % 10 == 0 && x != 0)) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        int revertedNumber = 0;\n        while (x > revertedNumber) {\n            int digit = x % 10;\n            revertedNumber = revertedNumber * 10 + digit;\n            x /= 10;\n        }\n\n        // Handle cases where the original number might be a palindrome\n        // even if revertedNumber is equal to it.\n        // For example: x = 1221\n        return x == revertedNumber || x == revertedNumber / 10;\n    }\n}\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"palindrome-number","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
